name: The Queen's Dreams: Expedition
description:
Canary sand dunes in the distance.
Wells of water strategically pitched next to every tent.
Brightly coloured and gold tasseled garments flung wildly in the air in the Market Square. 
Traders exchanged wears. 
Pick pockets roamed the vulnerable and the old men sat on benches swigging spirits and sharing tales.
But the excursion was to remain on track.
Following the star of her heart she neared closer. Arabian spices filled her lungs but true love filled her heart and led the way.
